ORIGINAL_TraitDefinition: The biovolume of resource consumed per unit mass of consumer per time
TraitUnit: cubic micrometer (cell wet biovolume) / (gram (body mass - wet) * 1 hour)
ResDensityUnit: cubic micrometer (wet cell biovolume) per milliliter
Citation: Seale D. B. and N. Beckvar. 1980. The Comparative Ability of Anuran Larvae (Genera: Hyla Bufo and Rana) to Ingest Suspended Blue-Green Algae. Copeia 1980:495-503.
